First start to initialise ROS in one console:

 - roscore &

In another console source the workspace:

 - source ./devel/setup.bash

In the same console start the main Publisher :

 - cd catkin_ws

 - rosrun Project_SOFT Main_Pub
 - python Server.py

In another console again start the Arduino to RPi conncetion script

 - cd catkin_ws/src/Project_SOFT/Script

 - rosrun Project_SOFT Arduino_to_RPi.py

Finally verify and flash the arduino 
